Tables.TableQueryDefinition: SELECT a.*,1 AS "PeriodID" FROM PULSE_vD_DimCargoType a

SELECT a.*,'Week ' || cast(Week_no as varchar(6)) AS "Unique Week",substr(WeekYYWW_No,5,2) AS "WeekWW_No",'W' || substr(WeekYYWW_No,5,2) AS "WeekWW_Name",CASE WHEN CaulatedWeekYear = Year_No THEN 0  WHEN CaulatedWeekYear > Year_No THEN 1 ELSE -1 END AS "WeekInDifferentYear" 
FROM  PULSE_vD_DimPeriod a

select * from (SELECT        cast(100 as smallint) AS SortOrder, cast('Current Period' as varchar(50)) AS TimeCalc_Name, 1 AS PeriodID) test
UNION ALL
select * from (SELECT        cast(200 as smallint) AS SortOrder, cast('YTD' as varchar(50)) AS Expr2, 4 AS Expr3) test2
UNION ALL
select * from (SELECT        cast(400 as smallint) AS SortOrder, cast('Last 4 Weeks' as varchar(50)) AS Expr2, 10 AS Expr3) test3
select * from (select 1 as ImportExport_Key,'Export' as ImportExport) a union all select * from (select 2 as ImportExport_Key,'Import' as ImportExport) a

SELECT  IS_COMPLETED
        FROM LabsFBRAAS_HSUD_V.HS_PULSE_tF_CYF_ShpEqp
       GROUP BY 1		
       
      UNION 
      SELECT * FROM (SELECT  CAST(-1 AS BYTEINT) AS IS_COMPLETED) a
